courses.title: AI Foundations: Understanding Machine Learning
courses.description: A beginner-friendly course that demystifies Machine Learning. Learn the concepts, terminology, and real-world impact of ML — no coding required. Ideal for decision-makers, students, and curious minds.

courses.title: Python for Machine Learning
courses.description: Learn Python the ML way. This course focuses on Python fundamentals with practical examples from data science and ML — lists, loops, NumPy, pandas, and plotting with Matplotlib.

courses.title: Math Essentials for ML: Linear Algebra & Statistics
courses.description: Get the math behind the machine. Focused on what matters most in ML: vectors, matrices, probability, statistics, and calculus — explained intuitively with interactive examples.
